==========
INSTALLATION
==========
To install the voronoi_library, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```
   git clone https://github.com/chr1shr/voro.git
   ```

2. Navigate to the cloned directory:
   ```
   cd voro
   ```

3. Build and install the library:
   ```
   make
   sudo make install
   ```

